> **Note** that the [configOverrides](../../installing/configuration.html#initconfiguration-deckhouse-configoverrides) parameter of the *InitConfiguration* resource is used when installing Deckhouse, not *ModuleConfig*.
>
> Set the `{{ include.moduleSnakeName }}Enabled: true` or `{{ include.moduleSnakeName }}Enabled: false` in the [configOverrides](../../installing/configuration.html#initconfiguration-deckhouse-configoverrides) parameter to explicitly enable or disable the module when installing Deckhouse.
